{"id":315007,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-常州精神病患者张荣富被刑拘（图）/","date":"2013-09-24T15:19:57Z","modified":"2013-09-24T15:19:57Z","title":"维权网 | 常州精神病患者张荣富被刑拘（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）常州市张荣富患有精神病，并领取了残疾人证。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日，张荣富的房屋被偷拆，其家属向茶山派出所报案，警察置之不理。患有精神病的张荣富受到此刺激，病情日益加重。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>点许，警察突然到张荣富的家要抓他，但没有发现张荣富在家。警察到处搜查，终于在居民楼附近找到张荣富，并将他抓走，未出示任何证件和法律文书。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张荣富的妻子万分焦急，担心其病情恶化。据了解，常州市天宁区茶山街道富强村委支部书记薛建兴向派出所报案，称张荣富到其家毁坏门窗和财物。为此，警察将精神病患者张荣富刑拘。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张荣富的妻子一再要求常州市公安局天宁分局茶山派出所出具刑拘的法律文书。该派出所于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日才向张荣富的妻子出具了《常州市公安局天宁分局（天公（茶）拘通字【</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>】</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">389</span><span>号）拘留通知书》称，我局将涉嫌毁坏公私财物罪的张荣富刑事拘留。但该《拘留通知书》不是原件，而是复印件；且在拘留决定之日起一个半月后才其家属领取《拘留通知书》复印件。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张荣富的妻子很伤心，自家的房屋被偷拆，向茶山派出所报案，警察置之不理。村委会书记薛建兴向派出所报案，警察只听一面之词。就将患精神病的丈夫刑拘。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>张荣富的妻子手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13382873631</span></div>\n<div><span>常州市公安局天宁分局局长金继英手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13775282345</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-3HcJ54V_hfU/UkGfx_dTV0I/AAAAAAAAolg/3rWh-Onlmlw/s1600/%E8%92%8B%E7%8E%89%E6%9A%96.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"214\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-3HcJ54V_hfU/UkGfx_dTV0I/AAAAAAAAolg/3rWh-Onlmlw/s320/%E8%92%8B%E7%8E%89%E6%9A%96.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-xZ_pnSVuEYM/UkGf3g-Y8KI/AAAAAAAAolo/OEEbxhjQn8c/s1600/%E8%92%8B%E7%8E%89%E6%9A%969.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-xZ_pnSVuEYM/UkGf3g-Y8KI/AAAAAAAAolo/OEEbxhjQn8c/s320/%E8%92%8B%E7%8E%89%E6%9A%969.JPG\" width=\"242\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}